<section id="readingText">
	<h1>Writing Task 1</h1>
  <p>You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
  <p><b>You missed an appointment at the immigration department because you were involved in an accident.</b></p>
  <p><b>Write a letter to the immigration officer. Apologise for missing the appointment and explain why you missed it. Ask if you can make a new appointment.</b></p>
	<p>You should write at least 150 words.</p>
	<p>You do&#xA0;<b>NOT</b>&#xA0;need to write your own address.</p>
	<p>Begin your letter as follows:</p>
	<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
</section>

<section id="body">
<ol id="splitquestionList">
	<li>Who do you have to write to?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t1">a relative</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t2">an acquaintance</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t3">a stranger</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t4">a friend</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t5">a colleague</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>
	  
	<li>What style of letter should you write?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t6">formal</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t7">informal</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What do you have to do in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t8">make a complaint</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t9">make an apology</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t10">give reasons</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t11">make a request</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t12">make an application</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	  

	<li>How many points do you have to cover in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t13">one</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t14">two</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t15">three</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t16">four</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t17">five</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	

	<li>Which of the following would it beappropriate to include in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t18">reference to the day and time of the original appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t19">reference to how long ago you made the original appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t20">the reason why you missed the appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t21">the reason you still want to see the immigration officer</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t22">a suggestion as to an alternative day and time for the appointment</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	

	<li>According to the writing task, what doyou have to ask in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t23">if you can cancel the appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t24">if you can rearrange the appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t25">if you can explain why you missed the appointment</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t26">if you can see a different immigration officer</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t27">if you need to make a new appointment</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	 
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	 
</ol>
